			<h3> Meaning</h3>

                    <p>
                         How do humans and language models compute meanings of words and sentences? What brain systems and computational processes do these processes use, and how do these systems support other aspects of human and animal cognition? 

			<h3> Metaphor</h3>

                    <p>
