                    </p>
			<h3> Systematicity</h3>

                    <p>
                         Words with similar meanings also tend to sound 
alike. Is this reflected in psychological processes? How can we use 
computational tools to discover regions of systematicity automatically?

                    </p>
			<h3> Grammar</h3>

                    <p>
                         Grammar choices convey meaning. Which choices convey which meanings?

                    </p>
